## How to Give Attribution

### For Unmodified Use

If you use this Software without modification, include the following notice in your project:

```markdown
## Credits

This project uses the Volume Sorted Coin List Generator by @comgunner.
Licensed under the Attribution License.
Repository: https://github.com/comgunner
```

### For Modified Versions

If you modify this Software, include the following notice:

```markdown
## Credits

This project is based on the Volume Sorted Coin List Generator by @comgunner.
Original repository: https://github.com/comgunner
Modified by: [Your Name/Organization]
Licensed under the Attribution License.
```

### For Integrated Use

If you integrate this Software into a larger project:

```markdown
## Third-Party Components

This project includes the following third-party software:

**Volume Sorted Coin List Generator**
- Author: @comgunner
- License: Attribution License
- Repository: https://github.com/comgunner
```

